Stats: 
Used for statistical aggregation i.e. minimum value, maximum value, average, summation, distinct count, normal count etc.

| stats <stats_function> as <name> by <field name>

Count:
| stats count by method

Minimum:
| stats min(status) by method

maximum:
| stats max(status) by method

average:
| stats avg(status) by method

sum: 
| stats sum(status) by method

distinct count:
| stats dc(status) by method

values:
| stats values(status) by method


we can use multiple stats function together.
